<?xml version="1.0" encoding="ISO-8859-1"?>
<refentry xmlns="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink" xmlns:svg="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:mml="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" xmlns:db="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook" version="5.0-subset Scilab" xml:lang="en" xml:id="aviinfo"><info><pubdate>April, 2006</pubdate></info><refnamediv><refname>aviinfo</refname><refpurpose>Get the information about video files. (experimental)</refpurpose></refnamediv>





<refsynopsisdiv><title>Calling Sequence</title><synopsis>info = aviinfo(filename)</synopsis></refsynopsisdiv>
<refsection><title>Parameters</title>
<variablelist>
   <varlistentry>
   <term>filename</term>
   <listitem>
   A string, the video filename to be read.
   </listitem>
   </varlistentry>
   <varlistentry>
   <term>info</term>
   <listitem>
   A mlist. The set of fields in the <literal>info</literal> structure is shown as follows:
    <informaltable border="1">
    <tr>
      <td>Field Name</td>
      <td>Description</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td>Filename</td>
      <td>String containing the video file name.</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td>FileSize</td>
      <td>Integer indicating the size of the video file in bytes.</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td>FramesPerSecond</td>
      <td>Integer indicating frames per second (FPS).</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td>Width</td>
      <td>Integer indicating frame width in pixels.</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td>Height</td>
      <td>Integer indicating frame height in pixels.</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td>NumFrames</td>
      <td>Integer indicating the number of frames in the video file.</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td>VideoCompression</td>
      <td>String containing the encoder name used to compress the video file.</td>
    </tr>
    </informaltable>


   </listitem>
   </varlistentry>
</variablelist>
</refsection>
<refsection><title>Description</title>
<para>
Video support for SIVP is only available when SIVP is compiled with OpenCV which support video I/O.
</para>
</refsection>

<refsection><title>Examples</title><programlisting role="example"><![CDATA[
	
    info = aviinfo(SCI+'/contrib/sivp/images/video.avi')

]]></programlisting></refsection>



